## BREAKTHROUGH: Scout Agent Discovery

### The Problem
- Only 14/65 junctions discovered per team in self-play (88x88 map, 13x13 obs)
- 72% of aligner time spent idle-scrambling (no frontier junctions)
- Aligner explore pattern only reaches 22 tiles from hub

### The Solution: Dedicated Scout Agent
Allocating 1 agent to permanently explore the map discovers far more junctions,
which the remaining agents can then align.

### Results (seed 0, 8 agents, 5000 steps)
